descriptions: [{"dateSeen":"2021-12-22T07:51:00.000Z","value":"Final Phase Release - Residence 1 North. The Luxury Collection at Windsor Row Townhomes by Electric Bowery Architects. A gated courtyard formed by two strikingly peerless structures create this new community of architectural residences. An abstract stream meanders along the axis of the landscaped courtyard. At entry level a direct entrance to a work-from-home office suite with bath, an outdoor patio and private 2-car garage plus storage. The main level features the great room with high ceilings, central fireplace and wall of glass that retracts to the balcony overlooking the courtyard. A modern kitchen with custom cabinetry, chef standard Thermador appliances, large kitchen island, pantry, powder room and dining area. Up the floating stairway from the main living level, we find two bedrooms with ensuite baths and laundry area. The upper level leads us to the large primary suite with walk-in closet, spa-like bath. Ascend to the roofline and encounter the expansive roof deck with living room, built-in kitchen, & alfresco dining perfect for outdoor entertaining. Enjoy 360 degree views of iconic LA; the Hollywood Sign, its historic hillside, snow capped mountains, the nearby spires of Koreatown and just beyond, DTLA. A neighborhood which knits the urbanity, nightlife, and diversity of K-town with the leafy grace of Windsor Square, Hancock Park & Larchmont Village.
